    "Participant age was distributed over three brackets, namely n = 2 were 30-39, n = 4 were 40-49, and n = 3 were 50-59.",
    "An inductive thematic analysis (Guest et al., 2011) of the answers to the open questions resulted in six themes discussed below.",
    "• Usability: the theme of usability underlines the system's ease of use and the need for clear instructions.",
    "Users mentioned the necessity for a \"user-friendly\" (P2) interface and highlighted the importance of having \"more instructions and more details need to be loaded\" (P1) to avoid confusion.",
